                        <incipit><cit>
                              <quote><supplied>M</supplied>iseremini mei <gap reason="editorial"/></quote>
                              <bibl>(Job 19:21) </bibl>
                           </cit> Istud uerbum est sancti Job qui dixit illud in afflictione sua positus</incipit>
                        <bibl>cf. Schneyer, VIII, p. 722 no. 85</bibl>
                        <note>Most of fol. 76v, and all of 77r, blank </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem n="4" xml:id="MS_Hamilton_51-part1-item4">
                        <locus from="77v" to="86v">(fols. 77v–86v)</locus>
                        <title key="work_14583" type="desc">Sermons</title>
                        <incipit><cit>
                              <quote><supplied>P</supplied>robet autem <gap reason="editorial"/></quote>
