                        <title key="work_14583" type="desc">Sermons from Christmas to Trinity Sunday</title>
                        <rubric><add> Sermones breues a nativitate domini usque ad festum sancte trinitatis</add>
                           <note>[table of contents]</note></rubric>
                        <msItem>
                           <note>First complete sermon:</note>
                           <incipit><cit>
                                 <quote>Parvulus natus est nobis <gap reason="editorial"/></quote>
                                 <bibl>(Isaiah 9:6)</bibl>
                              </cit> Circa nativitatem domini tria occurrunt notanda Primum est Christi humilitas</incipit>
                           <bibl>Schneyer VIII, p. 643 no. 6 (from <bibl subtype="external" type="ms">Munich Clm 9586</bibl>)</bibl>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem>
                           <locus from="214r" to="215ar">(fols. 214r–215ar)</locus>
