                              </cit> In tempore preterito peregimus festum patris festum filii festum spiritus sancti</incipit>
                           <bibl>Schneyer VIII, p. 646 no. 45 (from the same series in Clm 9586)</bibl>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem>
